---
title: Lamb Harissa Tacos with Spring Onion, Cheese and Potato Wedges
description: Ready in just half on hour, our lamb harissa tacos are guaranteed to spice up your weeknights in. Sweet and fragrant with a kick of heat,  harissa is the perfect partner for the rich taste of lamb. Serve with a side of golden potato wedges for a spec-taco-ular dinner time treat.
